name: Foodshare
body:
# Food Share 

-Proposal: users will be food mania that share activities such as cooking a delicious meal, hunging out for a famous cafe, commenting on one special dessert, creating heathy recipe and so on. They will post comment and news about what they like or dislike to socialize with other users. In this network, users can find popular food and its location and meet with friends who also love food.
